"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b29a1c6cece5c915a0457766dd8d06d430497b8","tid":1574042,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"大家唔好自滿，要繼續做文宣令更加多人支持"},{"pid":"ab49bcfbb4d50b72c76d13b207865d676af43fb3","tid":1574042,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"我老母終極和理非，一直唔支持暴力。<br />\n<br />\n但琴晚都改變咗，一路睇直播一路話啲示威者打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee91689a5588d021fd31be91a3651faa1e6ba48","tid":1574042,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2eeb4e4df9921e9b2d53cd3b9450a3490a1f157b","tid":1574042,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78bfe1ff81364fb1e2312c7011debac130de0ae1","tid":1574042,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"994054448fc81bd5e68a6ab1fbe86573c81394ea","tid":1574042,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤就係民意。<br />\n<br />\n沉默大多數平時好少會採取激進行動。但是，被不斷騷擾時，平時和平的人往往反應都會很大。<br />\n<br />\n點解政府失去民意，就係因為不斷撩交打，不斷點火頭，不斷推出政策惹起爭議。"}]}